571
00:32:13,732 --> 00:32:15,894
<i>Steven was immersed in post-production.</i>

572
00:32:16,001 --> 00:32:18,470
<i>Zanuck and Brown were onto something else.</i>

573
00:32:18,637 --> 00:32:22,164
<i>So they said to me at the end of March,</i>

574
00:32:22,274 --> 00:32:26,268
<i>"Can you do a book by the end of
May?" And with the folly of youth,</i>

575
00:32:26,378 --> 00:32:28,745
<i>I said, "Yeah, I can
