576
00:32:28,847 --> 00:32:31,179
<i>So I wrote the book in a very short time.</i>

577
00:32:31,283 --> 00:32:32,717
<i>Probably less than a month.</i>

578
00:32:32,818 --> 00:32:35,810
<i>And the original paperback
