01:35:56,918 --> 01:35:59,910
<i>Bambi goes on forever.
Snow White goes on forever.</i>

1743
01:36:00,021 --> 01:36:01,830
Jaws goes on forever.

1744
01:36:20,742 --> 01:36:24,269
<i>I certainly think that all of us
went through a survival adventure together,</i>

1745
01:36:24,412 --> 01:36:26,471
<i>the entire crew and cast and myself.</i>

1746
01:36:26,581 --> 01:36:30,791
<i>And I have very good memories in
many respects to the making of Jaws,</i>

1747
01:36:30,952 --> 01:36:32,761
<i>but I have many more bad memories.</i>

1748
01:36:33,221 --> 01:36:36,703
<i>Memories that still haunt my
nightmares, still wake me up sweating,</i>

1749
01:36:36,774 --> 01:36:39,323
but the bottom line is I'm grateful.

1750
01:36:39,594 --> 01:36:42,825
Because I went through
a kind of baptism of water.

1751
01:36:42,914 --> 01:36:48,398
And I came out of it, not only
alive, which was my main goal,

1752
01:36:48,503 --> 01:36:51,347
and getting through <i>Jaws</i> was
to come out of it in one piece,

1753
01:36:51,439 --> 01:36:53,248
but I came out of it with a career.

1754
01:36:53,524 --> 01:36:55,549
And I will forever be grateful,

1755
01:36:55,626 --> 01:36:58,994
no matter what I tell you
about those nightmares,

1756
01:36:59,163 --> 01:37:01,825
<i>to the fact that the dream
from the nightmare was</i>

1757
01:37:01,933 --> 01:37:04,777
<i>that I got a chance to make
any movie I wanted to make.</i>

1758
01:37:04,986 --> 01:37:07,899
<i>And that has continued to this day.</i>

1759
01:37:10,808 --> 01:37:16,326
Time will only tell when Jaws will
fade from the collective memory.

1760
01:37:16,848 --> 01:37:19,362
But I think as long <i>as</i>
there are sharks in the sea,

1761
01:37:19,467 --> 01:37:22,994
and as long as there are
oceans and bodies of water,

1762
01:37:23,187 --> 01:37:26,532
as long as there are kids with imagination

1763
01:37:26,641 --> 01:37:29,110
who like to torture and scare each other,

1764
01:37:29,193 --> 01:37:32,493
Jaws is going to be probably
around for a long time.

1765
01:40:55,132 --> 01:40:58,375
The shark is working.
Repeat. The shark is still working.

1766
01:40:58,486 --> 01:41:01,012
<i>Repeat.
The shark is still working.</i>

